<% content_for :title, "State Eligibility — Turf Totals" %>
<% content_for :meta_description, "Where Turf Totals is available. Excluded U.S. states, age requirements, and how location eligibility is enforced for our skill-based pick'em contests." %>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-10 px-2 space-y-12">
  <header>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-heading mb-2">State Eligibility</h1>
    <p class="text-secondary text-sm">Where you can play Turf Totals, and how we enforce it.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
      Turf Totals offers paid-entry contests of <strong>skill</strong>. State law on paid
      skill-based contests varies, so paid entry is not available everywhere. If you are located
      in an excluded state you may browse the site, but you cannot enter paid contests.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading">Excluded states</h2>
    <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
      Paid contest entry is currently <strong>not available</strong> in the following U.S. states:
    </p>
    <%= render "pages/excluded_states_list", excluded_states: @excluded_states %>
    <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
      This list is published directly from the same setting our enforcement system reads, and it
      may change as state law and guidance evolve. The list above is always current.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading">Age requirements</h2>
    <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
      You must be of legal age to participate in skill-based contests in your state:
      <strong>18 or older</strong> in most states, <strong>19+</strong> in Alabama and Nebraska,
      and <strong>21+</strong> in Iowa, Massachusetts, and Virginia. Every new account attests to
      this at signup.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading">How eligibility is enforced</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-body space-y-2">
      <li>
        We determine your approximate location by <strong>IP geolocation</strong> when you enter
        a contest or move funds. Users located in an excluded state are blocked from those actions.
      </li>
      <li>
        Using a VPN, proxy, or any other means to misrepresent your location violates our
        <%= link_to "Terms of Service", terms_path(anchor: "state-eligibility"), class: "text-primary hover:underline" %>
        and may result in account suspension and forfeiture of entries.
      </li>
      <li>
        If you believe you were blocked in error, contact
        <a href="mailto:alex@turfmonster.media" class="text-primary hover:underline">alex@turfmonster.media</a>
        and we will review it.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-2 text-sm text-secondary border-t border-subtle pt-6">
    <p>
      See also our
      <%= link_to "Terms of Service", terms_path, class: "text-primary hover:underline" %>,
      <%= link_to "Responsible Gaming", responsible_gaming_path, class: "text-primary hover:underline" %>
      page, and
      <%= link_to "Privacy Policy", privacy_path, class: "text-primary hover:underline" %>.
    </p>
  </section>
</div>
